ider.com%2Ffyre-festival-billy-mcfarland-released-from-prison-early-report-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereleased%20from%20prison%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20March%202022.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconvicted-fyre-festival-founder-billy-mcfarland-apologizes-in-gma-interview-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapologized%20for%20his%20actions%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20Good%20Morning%20America%20in%20November%202022%2C%20saying%20that%20what%20he%20did%20was%20%26quot%3Bwrong%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20let%20people%20down.%20I%20let%20down%20employees.%20I%20let%20down%20their%20families.%20I%20let%20down%20investors.%20So%20I%20need%20to%20apologize%2C%26quot%3B%20McFarland%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcFarland%2C%20however%2C%20was%20not%20done%20with%20the%20Fyre%20Festival%20just%20yet.%20In%20April%202023%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20now-deleted%20post%20on%20X%20that%20a%20sequel%20to%20the%20Fyre%20Festival%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffyre-festival-2-is-happening-billy-mcfarland-says-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinally%20happening%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcFarland%20initially%20announced%20in%20February%20that%20Fyre%20Festival%202%20would%20take%20place%20on%20Isla%20Mujeres%2C%20a%20Mexican%20island.%20The%20location%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20another%20Mexican%20tourist%20hot%20spot%2C%20Playa%20del%20Carmen%2C%20after%20the%20Isla%20Mujeres%20government%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20knowledge%20of%20this%20event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20event's%20organizers%20said%20the%20festival%20would%20not%20be%20held%20at%20Playa%20del%20Carmen%20either.%20The%20organizers%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20published%20on%20April%2016%20that%20the%20event%20was%20%26quot%3Bstill%20on%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bvett