%20surrounding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-mark-cuban-nyc-mayor-zohran-mamdani-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehis%20views%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Israel%20and%20tax%20hikes%20for%20the%20city's%20millionaires%20and%20billionaires%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20people%20who%20attended%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFresh%20off%20a%20primary%20win%20powered%20by%20the%20blunt%20message%20that%20New%20York%20is%20too%20expensive%2C%20Mamdani%20spent%20about%20an%20hour%20taking%20questions%20from%20New%20York's%20tech%20workers%20at%20an%20event%20hosted%20by%20the%20Partnership%20for%20New%20York%20City%2C%20Tech%3ANYC%2C%20and%20AlleyCorp%2C%20Ryan's%20venture%20capital%20firm%20that%20incubates%20and%20invests%20in%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20of%20some%20200%20people%20included%20startup%20founders%2C%20angel%20investors%2C%20and%20general%20partners%20from%20venture%20capital%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%2C%20held%20at%20a%20gleaming%20skyscraper%20in%20Midtown%2C%20offered%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20the%20candidate's%20grassroots%20campaign%2C%20which%20was%20built%20around%20free%20city%20buses%2C%20a%20freeze%20on%20New%20York%20rents%2C%20and%20tax%20hikes%20for%20millionaires.%20Mamdani%20leaned%20in%2C%20fielding%20questions%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20what%20attendees%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20characterized%20as%20%26quot%3Bcharisma%26quot%3B%20and%20pragmatism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20when%20someone%20in%20the%20audience%20raised%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20social%20media%20post%20about%20Mamdani%2C%20which%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20100%25%20Communist%20Lunatic%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Blooks%20TERRIBLE%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked%20that%20it%20must%20have%20hurt%20Mamdani%20to%20hear%20he%20looked%20lousy%2C%20drawing%20scattered%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20discussion%2C%20Mamdani%20and%20Ryan%20pinbal