%2C%26quot%3B%20Mamdani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaires-shouldnt-exist-zohran-mamdani-new-york-wealth-inequality-poverty-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20TV%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20seemed%20to%20be%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20business%20community%2C%20nonetheless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20have%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20CEOs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ryan%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20Tuesday%20meeting%20with%20New%20York's%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20meeting%2C%20Mamdani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2Fmamdani-clarifies-globalize-the-intifada-stance-in-meeting-with-business-elites-4bd47420%3Fmod%3Dhp_listb_pos1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20would%20not%20use%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bglobalize%20the%20intifada%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bdiscourage%26quot%3B%20others%20from%20doing%20so%2C%20after%20months%20of%20declining%20to%20condemn%20the%20phrase%20that%20some%20interpret%20as%20a%20call%20to%20violence%20against%20the%20Jewish%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Wednesday's%20event%2C%20one%20attendee%2C%20who%20works%20at%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20company%2C%20said%20he%20saw%20the%20candidate's%20rhetoric%20soften%20into%20a%20more%20pragmatic%20approach.%20The%20person%20said%20that%20when%20someone%20asked%20Mamdani%20what%20he%20hoped%20to%20achieve%20in%20his%20first%20hundred%20days%20in%20office%2C%20the%20candidate%20referenced%20a%202009%20proposal%20by%20then-Mayor%20Michael%20Bloomberg%20to%20make%20cross-town%20buses%20free.%20Mamdani%20has%20said%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20make%20every%20bus%20in%20New%20York%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20glad%20to%20see%20him%20being%20open%20to%20new%20ideas%20and%20working%20with%20people%20outside%20his%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yoni%20Rechtman%