%2C%20promised%20investors%20these%20%26quot%3BFrosties%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20sold%20for%20.04%20ETH%20or%20around%20%24200%20to%20%24300%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20featured%20in%20a%20game%20they%20were%20developing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20were%20also%20told%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Bbreed%26quot%3B%20their%20Frosties%20if%20they%20liked.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20purchased%20two%20or%20more%20Frosties%2C%20you%20could%20manufacture%20a%20miniature%20Frostie%20and%20get%20that%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20investors%20were%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20offering%20of%208%2C888%20Frosties%20NFTs%20sold%20out%2C%20Llacuna%20and%20his%20friend%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20also%2020%20%E2%80%94%20executed%20what's%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Brug%20pull.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20took%20down%20the%20Frosties%20webpage%20and%20its%20Twitter%20and%20Discord%20accounts%20and%20vanished%2C%20rendering%20Frosties%20essentially%20valueless%2C%20he%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20there%20was%20a%20negative%20reaction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELlacuna%2C%20who%20told%20the%20jury%20he%20became%20interested%20in%20crypto%20in%20Middle%20School%20and%20is%20now%20working%20as%20a%20hairstylist%2C%20is%20the%20fifth%20government%20witness%20to%20testify%20against%20Storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20expat%20faces%20more%20than%2040%20years%20in%20prison%20if%20convicted%20of%20conspiring%20to%20launder%20money%2C%20to%20run%20an%20unlicensed%20money-transfer%20company%2C%20and%20to%20violate%20federal%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20Storm%20made%20millions%20by%20knowingly%20helping%20crypto%20scammers%20and%20hackers%20hide%20their%20criminal%20proceeds.%20His%20customers%2C%20they%20say%2C%20included%20North%20Korea-backed%20hackers%20who%20used%20Tornado%20Cash%20to%20launder%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20stolen%20crypto%2C%20including%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3