one%20they've%20got%20who%20can%20show%20them%20how%20it's%20done.%20I%20don't%20want%20them%20walking%20into%20the%20world%20believing%20that%20a%20mother%2C%20a%20wife%2C%20or%20a%20business%20partner%20should%20be%20frantic%20and%20tired%2C%20always%20striving%20to%20meet%20someone's%20expectations.%20When%20they%20look%20at%20women%2C%20I%20want%20them%20to%20see%20their%20beauty%2C%20power%2C%20confidence%2C%20and%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20woman%20will%20never%20know%20that%20she%20changed%20my%20life.%20Six%20years%20later%2C%20I%20would%20be%20running%20a%20business%20rooted%20in%20helping%20high%20performers%20find%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20success.%20Every%20day%2C%20in%20every%20habit%2C%20I%20work%20to%20be%20a%20better%20human%20so%20I%20can%20be%20a%20better%20mother.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20four%20boys%20are%20along%20for%20the%20ride.%20They%20know%20every%20time%20I%20get%20the%20gig%20and%20every%20time%20I%20don't.%20They%20help%20me%20prep%20for%20speeches%20while%20I%20help%20them%20with%20spelling%20tests.%20We%20run%20through%20my%20P%26amp%3BL%20while%20studying%20geometry.%20If%20we%20want%20them%20to%20work%20hard%20for%20their%20dreams%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20it%20for%20ourselves%20first.%20And%20my%20husband%2C%20he's%20still%20here%2C%20playing%20a%20key%20role%2C%20as%20we%20grow%20alongside%20each%20other.%20On%20the%20outside%2C%20we%20are%20in%20the%20busiest%20season%20of%20our%20lives.%20On%20the%20inside%2C%20we%20have%20never%20been%20happier%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20when%20I'm%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20do%20it%20all%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20lead%20with%20the%20truth%2C%20which%20usually%20leads%20to%20a%20story%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20more%20humanness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flied-pregnant-woman-about-doing-it-all-a-working-mom-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publis