%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Motors%3C%2Fa%3E'%20Detroit-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-batteries-ai-cars-transport-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-batteries-ai-cars-transport-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evehicle%3C%2Fa%3E%20assembly%20plant%2C%20Factory%20Zero%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpenske-uses-ai-technology-to-enhance-truck-maintenance-cost-savings-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emachine%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20playing%20an%20increasingly%20significant%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI-based%20vision%20systems%20can%20swiftly%20identify%20maintenance%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20battery%20leaks%2C%20damaged%20metal%20components%2C%20and%20patchy%20paintwork.%20Marketing%20teams%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-marketing-strategy-platform-campaign-automation-copywriting-brand-content-clients-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20analyze%20consumer%20behavior%20and%20adapt%20their%20market%20research%20and%20promotional%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20General%20Motors%20looks%20to%20retain%20its%20crown%20as%20America's%20biggest%20car%20manufacturer%20amid%20increased%20competition%20from%20rivals%2C%20corporate%20leaders%20see%20AI%20as%20key%20to%20its%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e57a8d7-b6cd-4d07-b5f0-15b53773da54%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20customers%20where%20they%20are%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJon%20Francis%2C%20chief%20data%20and%20analytics%20officer%20at%20GM%2C%20said%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20contributing%20to%20change%20across%20the%20company.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20he%20said%2C%20AI%20is%20helping%20GM%20reach%20consumers%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20moment%26quot%3B%20on%20their%20car-buying%20journeys%2C%20enabling%20the%20carmaker%20to%20adjust%20production%20lines%20in%20%26quot%3Breal%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20data%20points%20like%20customer%20interactions%20and%20sales%20and%20manufacturing%20metrics%2C%20GM's%20AI%20solutions%20can%20provide%20insights%20on%20how%20to%20adjust%20production%20to%20ensure%20vehicles%20offer%20the%20features%20customers%20want%20most.%20Francis%20said%20examples%20include%20%26quot%3Bseamless%20connectivity%2C%26quot%3B%20safety%20features%20in%20tune%20with%20drivers'%20personal%20needs%20and%20those%20of%20their%20passengers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20traditional%20and%20electric%20engines.%20The%20AI%20solutions%20can%20also%20ensure%20anomalies%20are%20spotted%20and%20fixed%20before%20customers%20receive%20their%20new%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancis%20said%20the%20technology%20is%20also%20providing%20new%20GM%20customers%20with%20a%20more%20enjoyable%20driving%20experience.%20For%20example%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gm.com%2Fhome.detail.html%2FPages%2Ftopic%2Fus%2Fen%2F2025%2Fjan%2F0108-ai-ev.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGM%20is%20working%20with%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Pilot%20and%20EVgo%20to%20find%20the%20most%20optimal%20locations%20for%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%20enabling%20GM%20drivers%20to%20power%20up%20more%20easily.%20Decisions%20are%20made%20by%20algorithm-based%20analyses%20of%20traffic%20flow%20and%20nearby%20EV%20chargers%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20knowledge%20of%20human%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22022a4e1a-ddac-448b-898b-bdc73b1832b9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20look%20at%20the%20automotive%20landscape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGM's%20leaders%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20turning%20to%20AI%20to%20drive%20growth.%20The%20tech%20is%20making%20waves%20across%20the%20automotive%20sector%20more%20broadly.%20Research%20from%20Global%20Market%20Insights%20shows%20that%20AI%20automotive%20technology%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gminsights.com%2Findustry-analysis%2Fartificial-intelligence-ai-in-automotive-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%244.8%20billion%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20could%20reach%20%24186.4%20billion%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20evidenced%20by%20General%20Motors%2C%20AI%20is%20improving%20efficiencies%20on%20automotive%20production%20lines%20and%20in%20maintenance%20warehouses.%20But%20this%20technology%20is%20also%20delivering%20benefits%20for%20the%20end%20user%20by%20overhauling%20the%20driving%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyatt%20Mayham%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20IT%20consultancy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.qwoted.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnorthwest-ai-consulting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorthwest%20AI%20Consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20by%20embracing%20AI%20technologies%2C%20automotive%20companies%20may%20be%20able%20to%20design%20and%20sell%20%26quot%3Benhanced%20driver%20assistance%20systems%26quot%3B%20with%20features%20such%20as%20better%20automatic%20emergency%20braking%20and%20lane-keeping%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariq%20Munir%2C%20an%20AI%20transformation%20advisor%2C%20also%20envisages%20a%20bright%20future%20for%20AI%20automotive%20technologies.%20In%20particular%2C%20he%20expects%20to%20see%20automakers%20leverage%20%26quot%3Bsmart%2C%20self-optimizing%20systems%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20%26quot%3Benable%20production%20optimization%20and%20supply%20chain%20planning%20with%20near-perfect%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20automakers%20may%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20vehicle-testing%20costs%20by%20performing%20tests%20virtually%20by%20combining%20AI%20with%20immersive%20technologies%20like%20augmented%20and%20virtual%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20smart%20factory%20revolution%20in%20the%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20will%20enable%20a%20faster%2C%20cheaper%2C%20and%20more%20sustainable%20automotive%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d782683a-d4ea-464b-9065-ded563273b69%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarly%20obstacles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20success%20so%20far%2C%20GM's%20AI%20and%20ML%20transformation%20journey%20could%20face%20challenges.%20One%20was%20ensuring%20its%20AI%20solutions%20could%20deliver%20long-term%2C%20tangible%20benefits%20for%20all%20customers%2C%20which%20requires%20ample%20data.%20Therefore%2C%20Francis%20said%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20spent%20significant%20time%20implementing%20a%20robust%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-data-privacy-on-premises-information-technology-solutions-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIT%20infrastructure%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20collect%2C%20process%2C%20and%20analyze%20large%20datasets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20digital%20environment%20also%20had%20to%20be%20scalable%20from%20the%20beginning%20to%20facilitate%20the%20rapid%20expansion%20of%20AI%20adoption%20across%20GM's%20various%20departments%2C%20so%20Francis%20and%20his%20team%20built%20a%20%26quot%3Bscaled%20compute%20environment.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20a%20type%20of%20IT%20infrastructure%20that%20features%20self-adjusting%20compute%20resources%2C%20like%20processing%20power%20and%20storage%2C%20to%20cater%20to%20organizational%20and%20employee%20needs%20as%20they%20change%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResistance%20to%20change%20is%20another%20common%20pitfall%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prevent-employee-skepticism-push-back-gen-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20adoption%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20companies.%20Some%20workers%20are%20understandably%20concerned%20that%20AI%20could%20replace%20them%2C%20and%20usi