ers%20organize%20the%20development%20and%20building%20of%20data%20centers%20that%20meet%20a%20company's%20energy%20and%20cooling%20challenges.%20Sharma%20added%20that%20the%20plans%20can%20be%20customized%20for%20individual%20companies'%20requirements%20for%20their%20AI%20workloads%20in%20a%20more%20energy-efficient%2C%20sustainable%20way%20for%20the%20future.%20He%20said%20that%20data%20centers%20are%20already%20being%20built%20using%20the%20design%20created%20with%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20of%20the%20design%20is%20not%20to%20build%20a%20real-life%2C%20end-to-end%20replica%20of%20the%20design%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20to%20use%20various%20aspects%20of%20it%20to%20inform%20customers'%20initiatives%2C%20providing%20inspiration%20and%20guidance%20as%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fa336f8-f6ba-41ed-b193-42a791030b7a%5C%22%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20virtual%20modeling%20and%20testing%2C%20Sharma%20said%20that%20the%20reference%20designs%20developed%20with%20Nvidia%20could%20help%20data%20centers%20reduce%20cooling%20energy%20usage%20by%20about%2020%25.%20The%20plan%20can%20also%20help%20shorten%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20design%20and%20build%20new%20data%20center%20projects%20by%20about%2030%25%2C%20which%20also%20saves%20companies%20money%20and%20enhances%20sustainability%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20speed%2C%20it's%20cost%20and%20sustainability%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20pieces%20put%20together%20are%20an%20advantage%20for%20all%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchneider%20Electric%20plans%20to%20continue%20working%20with%20Nvidia%20to%20develop%20more%20reference%20designs%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20Sharma%20said.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20working%20to%20create%20data%20center%20designs%20and%20infrastructure%20that%20can%20accommodate%20even%