0still%20reign%20supreme%20if%20you%20want%20the%20very%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-noise-cancelling-headphones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20noise-canceling%20headphones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20these%20do%20an%20admirable%20job.%20I%20tested%20them%20against%20vacuum%20noise%2C%20caf%C3%A9%20chatter%2C%20and%20airplane%20cabin%20ambience%2C%20and%20they%20muffled%20each%20of%20those%20enough%20to%20keep%20annoyances%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20sensitive%20to%20head%20pressure%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20ANC%20is%20adjustable%2C%20or%20it%20can%20be%20adaptive%20to%20change%20with%20your%20environment.%20I%20usually%20left%20the%20headphones%20on%20their%20strongest%20setting%2C%20but%20the%20adaptive%20mode%20is%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20switching%20to%20the%20transparency%20mode%20to%20let%20outside%20sounds%20in%2C%20there's%20a%20breathy%20sound%20effect%20that%20gets%20whispered%20in%20your%20ears.%20It's%20creepy%20and%20a%20little%20unsettling.%20But%20the%20feature%20does%20provide%20good%20enough%20awareness%20to%20talk%20to%20others%20without%20voices%20sounding%20muted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECall%20quality%20is%20a%20highly%20touted%20feature%20of%20the%20Headphone%20(1)%2C%20but%20I%20was%20disappointed%20by%20it%20when%20used%20in%20a%20noisy%20environment.%20My%20voice%20sounded%20fine%20when%20used%20in%20a%20quiet%20place%2C%20but%20with%20street%20noise%20around%2C%20I%20found%20my%20voice%20to%20be%20highly%20artificial%20and%20easy%20to%20get%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22489405dd-344e-4204-9a9d-8e1ddcfdc057%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20them%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Nothing%20Headphone%20(1)%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221824%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20Nothing%20Headphone%20(1)%20over-ear%20headphones%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%2