nged%20the%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20simplest%2C%20solar%20drying%20is%20just%20using%20sunlight%20to%20remove%20moisture%20from%20crops%20%E2%80%94%20a%20way%20to%20keep%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20medicinal%20plants%20from%20going%20bad.%20Farmers%20have%20done%20it%20for%20generations%2C%20but%20the%20traditional%20method%20has%20its%20limits.%20Left%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20the%20produce%20gets%20hit%20by%20dust%2C%20insects%2C%20sudden%20rain%2C%20and%20harsh%20sunlight%20that%20can%20spoil%20both%20taste%20and%20quality.%20Industrial%20dryers%20solve%20these%20problems%20but%20come%20with%20high%20costs%20and%20require%20a%20steady%20electricity%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20something%20most%20rural%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171815.716_11zon-1752666509.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20low-cost%20solar%20dryer%20helps%20to%20preserve%20the%20excess%20produce%20of%20all%20kinds%20of%20crops%20without%20affecting%20the%20quality%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171815.716_11zon-1752666509.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171815.716_11zon-1752666509-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171815.716_11zon-1752666509-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171815.716_11z