20durable%20and%20better%20for%20insulation.%20The%20drying%20chamber%20is%20lined%20with%20UV-protective%20sheets%20that%20filter%20out%20harmful%20rays%2C%20shielding%20the%20produce%20from%20damage%20and%20keeping%20insects%20and%20pests%20at%20bay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20exhaust%20fan%2C%20powered%20by%20a%20small%20solar%20panel%2C%20ensures%20continuous%20airflow%20and%20removes%20excess%20moisture%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20an%20optimal%20drying%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20was%20balancing%20heat%20retention%20with%20proper%20airflow%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20innovator%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CToo%20much%20humidity%20would%20cause%20mould%2C%20but%20too%20little%20airflow%20would%20slow%20the%20drying%20process.%20We%20experimented%20with%20fan%20placement%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20layouts%20until%20we%20found%20the%20right%20balance.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20structure%20of%20the%20solar%20dryer%20is%20made%20using%20bamboo%20and%20wood%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20low%20for%20all%20farmers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T172025.910_11zon-1752666647-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471046%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20structure%20of%20the%20solar%20dryer%20is%20made%20using%20bamboo%20and%20wood%20to%20keep%20the%20cost%20low%20for%20all%20farmers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fan%20itself%20is%20repurposed%20from%20discarded%20computer%20or%20laptop%20parts%20%E2%80%94%20another%20small%20but%20significant%20touch%20that%20keeps%20costs%20low%20and%20makes%20the%20system%20more%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20solution%20that%20fits%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECost%20is%20a%20critical%20factor%20for%20rural%20farmers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20survive%20on%20modest%20incomes.%20Industrial%20dryers%20often%20cost%20lakhs%20%E2%80%94%20far%20beyond%20what%20smallholder%20farmers%20can%20afford.%20Swuyievezo%E2%80%99s%20solar%20dryer%20offers%20a%20much-needed%20alternative%3A%20affordable%2C%20customisable%2C%20and%20built%20from%20materials%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20strain%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20pocket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-foot%20model%20costs%20approximately%20Rs%207%2C000%2C%20while%20larger%20units%20measuring%2010%20by%2010%20feet%20range%20between%20Rs%2025%2C000%20and%20Rs%2030%2C000.%20The%20lower%20cost%20is%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20use%20of%20readily%20available%20materials%20such%20as%20bamboo%2C%20wood%2C%20aluminium%20cans%2C%20UV%20sheets%2C%20and%20solar%20panels%20%E2%80%94%20all%20chosen%20to%20reduce%20expenses%20without%20compromising%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C