-awareness-about-cancer-early-detection%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erebuild%20my%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20once.%E2%80%9D%20That%20line%20lingers%20long%20after%20we%20hang%20up%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20peace%20not%20as%20a%20vague%20aspiration%20but%20as%20a%20force%20strong%20enough%20to%20compel%20someone%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20lavish%20career%20and%20start%20afresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20forested%20valleys%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20he%20now%20lives%2C%20his%20story%20spins%20out%20like%20a%20river%20meandering%20through%20glens%20of%20hope%2C%20hardship%2C%20and%20heart.%20Not%20so%20long%20ago%2C%20he%20was%20earning%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20a%20year%20as%20creative%20director%20at%20a%20booming%20Hyderabad%20start%E2%80%91up%2C%20an%20achievement%20many%20only%20dream%20of%20in%20their%20twenties.%20Yet%2C%20despite%20the%20financial%20freedom%20and%20professional%20acclaim%2C%20he%20says%20the%20career%20felt%20%E2%80%9Chollow%2C%20like%20a%20gilded%20cage%20without%20room%20to%20breathe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20perched%20in%20these%20mountains%2C%20he%20is%20planning%20another%20farm.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20a%20replica%20of%20his%20previous%20endeavour%3B%20it%20will%20be%20a%20fresh%20start%2C%20grounded%20in%20everything%20he%20learnt%2C%20yet%20seeking%20something%20richer%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20community%20and%20belonging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20grounded%20beginnings%20of%20a%20dream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20began%20not%20in%20these%20cool%20heights%20but%20in%20the%20scorching%20heat%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20on%20a%20five%E2%80%91acre%20stretch%20of%20red%20clay%20that%20he%20painstakingly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F468218%2Fquit-mumbai-for-zero-waste-farm-mahabaleshwar-sustainable-farm-life-permaculture-handmade-products%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%