2C%20like%20mangoes%2C%20guava%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20mid%E2%80%91level%20nitrogen%20fixers%20such%20as%20moringa%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20grows%20fast%2C%20enriches%20soil%2C%20and%20feeds%20soil%20and%20people%20alike.%20It%20also%20had%20low%E2%80%91lying%20ground%20covers%20like%20sweet%20potato%2C%20sweet%20peas%2C%20butterfly%20pea%2C%20and%20brahmi%20to%20hold%20moisture%20and%20guard%20against%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20remained%20the%20fiercest%20challenge%20for%20the%20young%20boy%2C%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20life%20on%20a%20farm%20in%20the%20Obulapuram%20village%20near%20Pamidi.%20The%20well%20had%20dried%20up%2C%20and%20the%20stream%20flowed%20only%20in%20the%20monsoon.%20So%20he%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Neela%20Reddy%2C%20dug%20swales%2C%20trenches%20carved%20along%20the%20contours%20of%20the%20land%20to%20catch%20and%20hold%20rainwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20gruelling%20work%2C%20in%20the%20midday%20sun%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%2C%20pausing.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20the%20first%20monsoon%2C%20the%20soil%20drank%20deeply%20and%20the%20land%20greened.%E2%80%9D%20They%20installed%20drip%20irrigation%20for%20efficiency%2C%20and%20later%20added%20sprinklers%20for%20areas%20with%20dense%20ground%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20introduced%20chickens%20to%20scratch%20the%20soil%20and%20fertilise%20it%2C%20later%20brought%20in%20bees%20to%20aid%20with%20pollination%2C%20and%20added%20compost%20worms%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20breakdown%20of%20organic%20waste%20into%20nutrient-rich%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20grew%20a